metadata.name: earthquake
metadata.description:
Magnitude 7.8 and 7.5 earthquakes have hit southern Turkey. Thousands of people are still under the rubble and the rest are stranded on the streets in the cold.

100% of the proceeds will go to AFAD. You can donate directly to the official organization using the information below.
